<u><i>Bio:</i></u><br>
I am an associate professor of 
<a href="http://www.wheaton.edu/academics/programs/computerscience/i">Computer Science</a>
at <a href="http://www.wheaton.edu">Wheaton College (IL)</a>, having started
in the fall semester of 2004. 
I did my graduate work in 
<a href="http://www.cs.purdue.edu">Computer Science</a>
at <a href="http://www.purdue.edu">Purdue University<a>,
earning my M.S. in 2000 and my Ph.D. in 2004.
I graduated with a B.S. in mathematics and computer science
from <a href="http://www.calvin.edu">Calvin College</a> in 1998.<br> <br>
<a href="thomas-vandrunen-cv.pdf">My curriculum vitae</a>
